       <h1>
        Welcome to GLIDDON MARINE - Approved Yamaha Stockists
       </h1>
       <div class="clear">
       </div>
       <p>
        Freedom. Fun. Excitement. Adventure. Whatever you want from a personal watercraft you will find it with a Yamaha WaveRunner! Choose stand-up competition or freestyle action with the SuperJet, family fun with the award-winning VX1100 range, raw power from the race-inspired VX1800 R and S models or luxury blended with performance from the High Output and Super Vortex High Output FX and FX Cruiser's.  For those who crave ultimate performance there is the horizon-blurring, adrenalin-pumping power and acceleration from the outrageous supercharged and race-ready FZ SVHO series!
       </p>
       <p>
        No other watercraft has that special WaveRunner feeling - we know it as The Yamaha Difference - because over 25 years of dedication to technical innovation and development has delivered a wide line-up of class-leading models for you to take to the water on. A line-up packed with class-leading and industry-first features creating benefits you feel with every ride. Every detail of the technology and styling is designed to make you feel at one with your machine and in touch with the water you ride on. Which is what makes the Yamaha experience so utterly different. So completely unique.
       </p>
       <p>
        As authorised Yamaha Dealers Gliddon Marine hold 40 new and used WaveRunner models in stock and can arrange funding for your new WaveRunner using Yamaha Low Rate Finance (subject to availability). We can supply genuine Yamaha parts and accessories and carry out servicing and maintenance work in our workshop. We always have special offers on selected new skis and can arrange delivery anywhere in the UK. We are based in Torbay on the English Riviera.
       </p>
       <!--<p>Authorised Yamaha WaveRunner dealer Gliddon Marine are holding an open event the weekend of Saturday 17th &amp; Sunday 18th May from their dealership in Torbay! There will be a comprehensive line-up of 2014 WaveRunner models to view, all available with Yamaha low-rate finance. We'll also have some very special deals on new pre-2014 models, all with 3 years 0% finance!</p>
         <p>Also on display, a selection of quality pre-owned WaveRunners from as little as &pound;2,995. If you'd like to view the new models/discuss the special offers available why not come along? The friendly team will be on hand to give help and advice on all aspects of buying and owning a Yamaha WaveRunner plus RYA training courses and WaveRunner experiences.</p>
         <p>On Sunday 18th, a limited number of WaveRunners will be available for demonstration from Brixham Marina by prior appointment, including the mighty new FZS SVHO and FX Cruiser SVHO (participants must hold and produce RYA PW proficiency certificate for these models).</p>-->
